snippet.title: Mangs
snippet.description:
Let's Player, Shitposter, Advance Wars & Fire Emblem Enthusiast. My name is Mangs, and this is one of the most popular Advance Wars & Fire Emblem channels on YouTube.

I release videos daily on this channel. My content ranges from simple Let’s Plays to more informative and heavily edited videos, I also do the occasional shitposts. My videos are typically released in the afternoon around 18:00-21:00 CET, so depending on where you live, there should always be a video ready for when you come home from school/work to relax.

I am very easy to get in contact with. You can send me a mail at mangsmemes@gmail.com with any questions. If you want to ask for permission to use my videos in your content, you may do so freely as long as you credit me and link to my channel.

Enjoy your stay!
